# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# TURN SERVERS — pick ONE option below
# Without TURN, calls only work on same WiFi!
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

# OPTION A: Metered.ca (FREE — recommended, easiest)
# 1. Go to https://www.metered.ca/stun-turn  →  sign up free
# 2. Create an app  →  copy App Name + API Key
# 3. Paste here:
